ibit an application of this new tool in which we approximate\nthe persistence diagram of a filtration of Rips complexes where vertex\ncollapses are used to tame the blow-up in size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2012 17:46:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2012 16:40:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2013 15:22:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 25 Mar 2014 17:26:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-26"}
